{"tid":2436088,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"我家婆婆腦退化｜孫女棄全職教父母照顧97歲婆婆 試着成人尿片自學護老「點解重擔要一個人承擔」","createTime":"2021-03-06T20:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T11:35:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1af381bde3a7fbd5b4ab0279f67c65c91b6949b9","tid":2436088,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T20:41:02.000Z","msg":"孫女寧做Freelancer 專心照顧97歲腦退化婆婆<br />\n張靜文(文文)的婆婆97歲，確診中度認知障礙。文文爸爸：「佢個性格坐唔定，12年前八十幾歲仲行動自如周圍去玩，嗰日佢追地鐵跌親昏迷，醒來就失去自理能力，要坐輪椅。」文文很疼婆婆的，近年她由全職活動搞手轉做Freelancer，與七十多歲的爸媽，工人姐姐一起照顧婆婆。還寫了專頁 《我家有個大BB》，分享與婆婆的生活趣事及護老資訊。早陣子她就親身試穿尿片，寫晒心得貼士，統計埋尿片花費，要幫婆婆找出舒服的穿片法，幫照顧者們省錢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210307/HFWVIRBPOFDUZEB762CND54LGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210307%2FHFWVIRBPOFDUZEB762CND54LGQ%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=bd0f956a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210307%2FHFWVIRBPOFDUZEB762CND54LGQ%2F&h=57f14e53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210307/HFWVIRBPOFDUZEB762CND54LGQ/</a>"},{"pid":"a339423dcc5bfa2516ed2bd11750f18a4dd4afd1","tid":2436088,"uid":325346,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T20:48:16.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n要照顧三個老人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83b5b416a0e855893ed04dc65406925cdd63c53","tid":2436088,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"022bf675214f7a58943372e766e7e0ec954ab21d","tid":2436088,"uid":118675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f081ee3d4cbeede1065fffdf44ac61cc5b54d7f","tid":2436088,"uid":5943,"like":5,"d